song_lyrics: Fūlḍā dhārī re, ange fūlḍā dhārī,
Shobhe Shāmaḷiyo sujāṇ ange fūlḍā dhārī... °ṭek
Māthe bhramar gunjār karī āve chhe orā... Fūlḍā° 1
Haiḍā upar hār sundar fūlnā pe’rī,
Chore mānaniyonā manane pyāro, laṭakāḷo le’rī... Fūlḍā° 2
Ati ānand vadhāre nitya Dharmano Lālo... Fūlḍā° 3
Gopī ango-ang fūlī rahī Shāmaḷā sange... Fūlḍā° 4
title: Fūlḍā dhārī re ange fūlḍā dhārī
